These are the variables that do not fit into any coherent periodic class, not even IRR. They would be classified as "dubious" except that they have ddcSTAT=1, meaning that detections on the difference images demonstrate their genuine variability. Their physical nature is unclear, but many of them do appear to exhibit highly significant stochastic variations with very little coherence on the timescales probed by ATLAS (Heinze+, 2018); galactic plane
